{
  "translations": [
    { "resource_id": 149, "text": "Woe to every slandering backbiter," },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "who <span class=\"h\">hoarded<sup foot_note=\"81496\">1</sup> </span>wealth and counted it over,"
    },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "thinking that his wealth has made him immortal."
    },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "But no! He will surely be thrown into the Crusher."
    },
    {
      "resource_id": 149,
      "text": "And what can make you realize what the Crusher is?"
    },
    { "resource_id": 149, "text": "Allah’s kindled Fire" },
    { "resource_id": 149, "text": "that mounts over burning hearts." },
    { "resource_id": 149, "text": "Indeed, it is over them with no exit," },
    { "resource_id": 149, "text": "in extended columns." }
